## Image 3: Tea Smoking in Action
Style: Photorealistic food photography, dramatic action shot
Subject: A wok setup on a stove with tea smoking in progress — billowing fragrant smoke rises from the wok (rice, sugar, and black tea leaves smoking), a wire rack with tofu visible inside, the smoke creating beautiful atmospheric swirls, kitchen steam and smoke catching the light
